m-banner-1\"><span id=\"div-gpt-ad-cultofmac_com-banner-1-0\" ezaw=\"580\" ezah=\"400\" style=\"position:relative;z-index:0;display:inline-block;min-height:400px;min-width:580px;\" class=\"ezoic-ad\"></span></span>\n      <!-- End Ezoic - under_second_paragraph 113 - long_content -->\n    </div>\n    <p>The rest of us will be able to enjoy the first three episodes of <em>For All Mankind</em> on November 1, when TV+ makes its debut in more than 100 countries. New episodes will be added weekly, every Friday.</p>\n    <p><span id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-193\" class=\"ezoic-adpicker-ad\" data-ezadpicker=\"193\" data-ez-position-type=\"longest_content\"></span><!-- placeholder 193 blocked.  Reason : no sizes -->Other Apple originals debuting on that date include <em>The Morning Show, See, Dickinson, Little America,</em> and <em>Home Before Dark.</em></p>\n    <div class=\"code-block code-block-4\" style=\"margin: 8px 0; clear: both;\">\n      <!-- Ezoic - under_second_paragraph 191 - long_content -->\n      <span id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-191\"></span><!-- placeholder 191 blocked.  Reason : no sizes -->\n      <!-- End Ezoic - under_second_paragraph 191 - long_content -->\n\n    </div>\n\n    <p>A Tuesday report revealed <a href=\"https://www.cultofmac.com/659184/apple-tv-second-season-for-all-mankind-see-dickinson/\">Apple has already ordered a second season of the show</a>, which is now in production. Apple has also ordered <em><a href=\"https://www.cultofmac.com/658974/jason-sudeikis-ted-lasso-comedy-apple-tv/\">Ted Lasso</a>,</em> a new comedy series starring Jason Sudeikis.</p>\n    <h3>TV+ will cost just $4.99</h3>\n    <p>Apple TV+ will offer only a handful of shows at launch — far fewer than competitors like Netflix. But it will cost just $4.99 a month for up to six family members.<span id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-615\" class=\"ezoic-adpicker-ad\" data-ezadpicker=\"615\" data-ez-position-type=\"longer_content\"></span></p>\n    <div class=\"code-block code-block-5\" style=\"margin: 8px 0; clear: both;\">\n      <!-- Ezoic - mid_content 192 - longer_content -->\n      <span id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-192\"></span><!-- placeholder 192 blocked.  Reason : no sizes -->\n      <!-- End Ezoic - mid_content 192 - longer_content -->\n    </div>\n\n    <p>Anyone who picked up a new Apple device this fall, after iPhone 11 was unveiled, <a href=\"https://www.cultofmac.com/650658/buy-a-new-apple-device-and-youll-get-1-year-free-apple-tv/\">will get the first year free</a>.</p>\n    <p>Despite the small number of shows, TV+ has attracted major Hollywood stars. Jennifer Aniston, Reece Witherspoon, Steve Carrel, Jason Momoa, and Oprah are all on board.</p>\n    <div class=\"ctx-sidebar-container ctx-sidebar-container--QJvt15zw9rajZ808EbEKV46VwRv2iPeh\"></div>\n\n    <div class=\"ctx-subscribe-container ctx-personalization-container ctx_default_placement ctx-clearfix\"></div>\n    <div class=\"ctx-social-container ctx_default_placement ctx-clearfix\"></div>\n    <div class=\"ctx-module-container ctx_default_placement ctx-clearfix\"></div><span class=\"ctx-article-root\"><!-- --></span>\n    <div class=\"code-block code-block-12\" style=\"margin: 8px 0; clear: both;\">\n      <!-- Ezoic - long_content 149 - longest_content -->\n      <span id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-149\"></span>\n      <!-- End Ezoic - long_content 149 - longest_content -->\n    </div>\n    <span id=\"ezoic-pub-ad-placeholder-127\" class=\"ezoic-adpicker-ad\" data-ezadpicker=\"127\" data-ez-position-type=\"incontent_8\"></span><span style=\"display:block !important;float:none;margin-bottom:10px !important;margin-left:0px !important;margin-right:0px !important;margin-top:10px !important;min-height:400px;min-width:580px;text-align:center !important;\" class=\"ezoic-ad large-mobile-banner-1 adtester-container adtester-container-127\" data-ez-name=\"cultofmac_com-large-mobile-banner-1\"><span id=\"div-gpt-ad-cultofmac_com-large-mobile-banner-1-0\" ezaw=\"580\" ez